Kostos is a Greek boy whom Lenaâ€™s grandmother selects as a perfect match for Lena. Kostos is handsome and kind, and he was raised in Greece after his parents and brother were killed in a car accident in the United States. When Kostos accidentally sees Lena skinny-dipping, Lena thinks he was spying on her, and she inadvertently suggests to her grandparents that Kostos attacked her. Kostos is in love with Lena, and they kiss before she leaves Greece.